<span id="freeTextContainer14176886931066067960">The Steppe- 4/5 stars (just straight vibes)<br/><br/>The Duel - 3/5<br/><br/>The Story of an Unknown Man- 5/5<br/><br/>Three Years - 1/5 (either this went way over my head or what is this actually about??? Seems to be basically focused on the fact life is miserable and a lot of that misery can happen in a relatively short space of time, like a span of 3 years)<br/><br/>My Life - 3.5/5 </span>

