<li class='cover' id='bookCover_252981'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/252981.The_Collected_Tales_of_Nikolai_Gogol"><img alt="The Collected Tales of Nikolai Gogol" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1403184138l/252981._SX98_.jpg" />
